### ==========================================================================
### SendAPI External API — HTTP Client Examples
### ==========================================================================
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000/api/v1
### Auth: Bearer sk_live_...
### ==========================================================================


### ==========================================================================
### 1. USERS
### ==========================================================================

### Create a user
POST {{ base_url }}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "external_user_id": "user_12345",
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "language": "en"
}

### List users (paginated)
GET {{ base_url }}/users?page=1&per_page=20
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}

### Get a single user
GET {{ base_url }}/users/48
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}

### Delete a user from the organization
DELETE {{ base_url }}/users/48
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}

### Generate a claim token (account linking URL)
POST {{ base_url }}/users/48/claim-token
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}


### ==========================================================================
### 2. ACCOUNTS
### ==========================================================================

### List connected accounts for a user
GET {{ base_url }}/users/48/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}

### Connect a YouTube account (returns OAuth URL)
POST {{ base_url }}/users/48/accounts/youtube/connect
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}

### Connect a Telegram channel (requires bot to be added as admin first)
POST {{ base_url }}/users/48/accounts/telegram/connect
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel_id": "@your_channel_username"
}

### Connect a TikTok account
POST {{ base_url }}/users/48/accounts/tiktok/connect
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}

### Connect an Instagram account
POST {{ base_url }}/users/48/accounts/instagram/connect
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}

### Disconnect an account
DELETE {{ base_url }}/users/48/accounts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}


### ==========================================================================
### 3. POSTS
### ==========================================================================

### Upload a media file directly to the server
POST {{ base_url }}/upload/file
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="data"; filename="video.mp4"
Content-Type: video/mp4

< /path/to/video.mp4
--boundary--

### Create a post (URL-based media — worker downloads from URL)
POST {{ base_url }}/users/48/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My awesome video",
  "description": "Check this out!",
  "tags": ["tech", "tutorial"],
  "platforms": ["youtube"],
  "media_type": "video",
  "media_source": "/tmp/sendapi/bf39ff5b-aea4-4058-889f-72754ee83ddf.mp4"
}

### Create a post (photo to multiple platforms)
POST {{ base_url }}/users/48/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Beautiful sunset",
  "description": "Captured this evening",
  "tags": ["photography", "nature"],
  "platforms": ["instagram", "facebook", "telegram"],
  "media_type": "photo",
  "media_source": "https://your-cdn.com/sunset.jpg"
}

### Create a post with TikTok settings
POST {{ base_url }}/users/48/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Dance challenge",
  "platforms": ["tiktok"],
  "media_type": "video",
  "media_source": "https://your-cdn.com/dance.mp4",
  "platform_settings": {
    "tiktok": {
      "privacy_level": "PUBLIC_TO_EVERYONE",
      "allow_comment": true,
      "allow_duet": false,
      "allow_stitch": false,
      "branded_content": false,
      "music_usage_confirmed": true
    }
  }
}

### Create a post to specific accounts only
POST {{ base_url }}/users/48/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Targeted post",
  "platforms": ["youtube"],
  "media_type": "video",
  "media_source": "https://your-cdn.com/video.mp4",
  "target_account_ids": [1, 2]
}

### List posts (paginated)
GET {{ base_url }}/users/48/posts?page=1&per_page=20
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}

### List posts filtered by status
GET {{ base_url }}/users/48/posts?post_status=success
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}

### List failed posts
GET {{ base_url }}/users/48/posts?post_status=failed
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}

### Get a single post
GET {{ base_url }}/users/48/posts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}


### ==========================================================================
### 4. WEBHOOKS
### ==========================================================================

### Register a webhook
POST {{ base_url }}/webhooks
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://your-app.com/webhooks/sendapi",
  "events": ["post.completed", "post.failed"]
}

### Register a webhook for all events
POST {{ base_url }}/webhooks
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://your-app.com/webhooks/sendapi",
  "events": ["post.completed", "post.failed", "post.processing", "account.disconnected"]
}

### List webhooks
GET {{ base_url }}/webhooks
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}

### Update a webhook (change URL)
PATCH {{ base_url }}/webhooks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://new-url.com/webhooks/sendapi"
}

### Update a webhook (change events)
PATCH {{ base_url }}/webhooks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "events": ["post.completed"]
}

### Disable a webhook
PATCH {{ base_url }}/webhooks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "is_active": false
}

### Re-enable a webhook (resets failure counter)
PATCH {{ base_url }}/webhooks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "is_active": true
}

### Delete a webhook
DELETE {{ base_url }}/webhooks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}


### ==========================================================================
### 5. ORGANIZATION
### ==========================================================================

### Get organization info (quota, usage, rate limits)
GET {{ base_url }}/org
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}

### Create a new API key
POST {{ base_url }}/org/api-keys
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Production"
}

### List API keys (prefix only, never full key)
GET {{ base_url }}/org/api-keys
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}

### Revoke an API key
DELETE {{ base_url }}/org/api-keys/1
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}

### Get branding assets (badge URL + landing URL)
GET {{ base_url }}/org/branding
Authorization: Bearer {{ api_key }}
